        <xs:annotation>
          <xs:documentation>The requestPermissionId is energy data space specific identification attribute holding an unique identifier issued by the energy data space to allow for tracing of the permission through serveral message exchanges.
Note: the requestPermissionId is NOT the identifier issued by the Identity Service Provider as specified in the EU Implementing Act on access to Metering and Consumption Data.</xs:documentation>
