        <xs:annotation>
          <xs:documentation>defaultValues is a energy data space specific attribute to hold relevant default values. The format to use can freely be chosen based on the implementation. Most commonly you would expect a semi-colon separated name value pair, like: "minPower=value; maxPower=value; avgPower=value".</xs:documentation>
          <xs:documentation cimp:category="TagValue" cimp:subcategory="ESMPRG">6</xs:documentation>
